   Photo Profile
   Take a look at some of the highlights from Mrs. Bush's initiatives and
   activities through this photo essay and a Holiday Cheer photo essay.
   White House photo by Moreen Ishikawa.
   Education Initiatives
   Mrs. Bush's education initiatives include recruiting more people to
   join the teaching profession and helping to ensure children start
   school ready to read and learn.
   National Book Festival, September 8
   Laura Bush hosted the first National Book Festival at the Library of
   Congress on September 8. The event included readings, book signings,
   storytelling, and tours of the Library.
   U.S. History: First Ladies Gallery
   Who was the First Lady at the the turn of the last century? Visit the
   First Ladies' Gallery to find out about the outstanding women who have
   served as First Lady of the United States.

